    "These parameters are then used to optimize network configurations, thereby enhancing network usage efficiency and service quality in NDTs.",
    "To overcome the associated challenges including data heterogeneity, balancing personalization with generalization, and maintaining data privacy, data standardization and ML algorithms can be used for handling and interpreting diverse data.",
